title: For Sale/Trade:  New/Unfired AR-15 *Revised*
postcontent:
For sale is a new and unfired AR-15.  Upper is Doublestar Arms (DSA), lower is API (Aero-Precision, whom used to manufacture parts for Armalite before going into their own business.  I know that this technically makes this a 'franken-AR', so if you're looking for a rifle to hang on a display, this isn't your rifle.  If you're looking for a rifle that is durable, reliable, and which can put years worth of rounds downrange, this *is* your rifle.  

Barrel is 1:9 twist, optomized for 55 gr (approximately) rounds, but will still handle lighter or heavier rounds with more than acceptable downrange accuracy, and is chrome molly-coated for added durability.  Upper is chambered for 5.56x45, so will easily handle either .223 or the hotter 5.56 depending on your preference.  Lower is multi-cal marked, with pictograph safety selector symbols (think HK rifles).  

Will also include one USGI 30-round magazine to get you shooting sooner!  Standard M-4 furniture, and can include a Rock River Arms carry-handle for an extra $50 if that's your sighting preference.  Will consider partial trades, but only if they are of exceptional value because I'm really looking for more of a cash deal on this one.  Thank you for your time, and don't hesitate to shoot me an offer.
